      <title>从零开始学Java01:Java的基础概念（所用版本：JDK17）</title>
      <link href="/2023/12/29/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AD%A6Java%EF%BC%9AJava%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/"/>
      <url>/2023/12/29/%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AD%A6Java%EF%BC%9AJava%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>​</p><h1 id="从零开始学Java01-Java的基础概念（所用版本：JDK17）"><a href="#从零开始学Java01-Java的基础概念（所用版本：JDK17）" class="headerlink" title="从零开始学Java01:Java的基础概念（所用版本：JDK17）"></a>从零开始学Java01:Java的基础概念（所用版本：JDK17）</h1><p>学习视频：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV17F411T7Ao">黑马程序员Java零基础视频教程</a></p><h2 id="一、注释"><a href="#一、注释" class="headerlink" title="一、注释"></a>一、注释</h2><p><strong>添加注释仅仅是为了对代码进行解释说明，不参与程序编译。</strong>  </p><h3 id="1-注释分为三种类型："><a href="#1-注释分为三种类型：" class="headerlink" title="1. 注释分为三种类型："></a>1. 注释分为三种类型：</h3><ol><li>单行注释 具体格式为：&#x2F;&#x2F;注释内容</li><li>多行注释 具体格式为：&#x2F;*   *&#x2F;</li><li>文档注释 具体格式为：&#x2F;**   *&#x2F;</li></ol><h2 id="二、关键字"><a href="#二、关键字" class="headerlink" title="二、关键字"></a>二、关键字</h2><p><strong>关键字是被Java赋予了特定含义的英文单词</strong></p><h3 id="1-关键字的特点"><a href="#1-关键字的特点" class="headerlink" title="1. 关键字的特点:"></a>1. 关键字的特点:</h3><ol><li>关键字的字母全部小写</li><li>常用的代码编辑器，针对关键字有特殊的颜色标记，非常直观</li></ol><h3 id="2-关键字class"><a href="#2-关键字class" class="headerlink" title="2. 关键字class"></a>2. 关键字class</h3><p>class：用于创建&#x2F;定义一个类，类是Java最基本的组成单元<br>例如：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Helloworld</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="comment">//此处定义了一个名为HelloWorld的类</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、字面量"><a href="#三、字面量" class="headerlink" title="三、字面量"></a>三、字面量</h2><p><strong>字面量：用于告诉程序员数据在程序中的书写格式（与C语言中的数据类型相似）</strong></p><h2 id="1-字面量类型"><a href="#1-字面量类型" class="headerlink" title="1. 字面量类型"></a>1. 字面量类型</h2><ol><li>整数类型：不带小数点的数字，如123，-456；</li><li>小数类型：带小数点的类型，如1.2，-1.3；</li><li>字符串类型：用双引号括起来的内容，如”HelloWorld”；</li><li>字符类型：用单引号括起来的内容，内容只能有一个，如’A’,’0’；</li><li>布尔类型：布尔值，表示真假，只有两个之true和false；</li><li>空类型 ：一个特殊的指，空值，null。</li></ol><h2 id="2-示例"><a href="#2-示例" class="headerlink" title="2.示例"></a>2.示例</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ValueDemo1</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//整数</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="number">123</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(-<span class="number">456</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//小数</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="number">1.2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(-<span class="number">1.3</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;HelloWorld&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;从零开始学Java&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//字符</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&#x27;男&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//布尔类型</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="literal">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="literal">false</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//空类型</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//细节：null不能直接打印，如需打印则应该用字符串形式进行打印</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;null&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注：关于cmd窗口编译Java文件注释处出现乱码的解决方案</strong><br>我在此处使用cmd进行Java文件编译时，发现作为注释的文字出现了乱码问题，我在上网查询后发现解决办法如下：<br>将文件重新保存为ANSI编码即可正常进行编译运行，具体参考来源<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_64482460/article/details/126200586">链接</a></p><h2 id="3-特殊字面量：制表符-t"><a href="#3-特殊字面量：制表符-t" class="headerlink" title="3.特殊字面量：制表符&#x2F;t"></a>3.特殊字面量：制表符&#x2F;t</h2><p>其作用是在打印的时候把前面字符串的长度补齐到8或者8的整数倍。最少补1个空格，最多补8个空格。</p><p>如：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">HelloWorld</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>+<span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>+<span class="string">&quot;age&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;tom&quot;</span>+<span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>+<span class="string">&quot;23&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打印结果为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">name    age</span><br><span class="line">tom     23</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="四、变量"><a href="#四、变量" class="headerlink" title="四、变量"></a>四、变量</h1><p><strong>变量：用于记录值经常发生变化的数据</strong></p><h2 id="1-变量的定义格式"><a href="#1-变量的定义格式" class="headerlink" title="1.变量的定义格式"></a>1.变量的定义格式</h2><p><strong>数据类型 变量名 &#x3D; 数据值；</strong></p><p>数据值：存在空间里面的数值<br>变量名：变量的名字<br>数据类型：为空间中存储的数据加入【类型】限制</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableDemo1</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//主入口</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//定义变量</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-变量的使用方式"><a href="#2-变量的使用方式" class="headerlink" title="2.变量的使用方式"></a>2.变量的使用方式</h2><ol><li>输出打印<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>参与计算<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">b</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a + b);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>修改变量记录的值<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="number">50</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="3-变量的注意事项"><a href="#3-变量的注意事项" class="headerlink" title="3.变量的注意事项"></a>3.变量的注意事项</h2><ol><li>只能存一个值<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>，b = <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>变量名不允许重复定义</li><li>一条语句可以定义多个变量</li><li>变量在使用之前一定要进行赋值</li><li>变量的作用域范围</li></ol><h2 id="4-变量练习，计算公交车人数"><a href="#4-变量练习，计算公交车人数" class="headerlink" title="4.变量练习，计算公交车人数"></a>4.变量练习，计算公交车人数</h2><p>一辆公交车，司机不计入人数，一开始没有乘客。<br>第一站：上去一位乘客；<br>第二站：上去两位乘客，下来一位乘客；<br>第三站：上去两位乘客，下来一位乘客；<br>第四站：下来一位乘客；<br>第五站：上去一位乘客。<br>请问：到了终点站，车上一共几位乘客。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableTest</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//一开始没有乘客。 </span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">count</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//第一站：上去一位乘客； </span></span><br><span class="line">         count = count + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//第二站：上去两位乘客，下来一位乘客；</span></span><br><span class="line">        count = count + <span class="number">2</span> - <span class="number">1</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//第三站：上去两位乘客，下来一位乘客；  </span></span><br><span class="line">        count = count + <span class="number">2</span> - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//第四站：下来一位乘客；</span></span><br><span class="line">        count = count - <span class="number">1</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//第五站：上去一位乘客。</span></span><br><span class="line">        count = count + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(count);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="五、计算机中的数据存储"><a href="#五、计算机中的数据存储" class="headerlink" title="五、计算机中的数据存储"></a>五、计算机中的数据存储</h1><h2 id="1-二进制的运算过程"><a href="#1-二进制的运算过程" class="headerlink" title="1.二进制的运算过程"></a>1.二进制的运算过程</h2><p>逢二进一，借一当二</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">十进制</th><th align="center">二进制</th><th align="center">十进制</th><th align="center">二进制</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">0</td><td align="center">0</td><td align="center">5</td><td align="center">101</td></tr><tr><td align="center">1</td><td align="center">1</td><td align="center">6</td><td align="center">110</td></tr><tr><td align="center">2</td><td align="center">10</td><td align="center">7</td><td align="center">111</td></tr><tr><td align="center">3</td><td align="center">11</td><td align="center">8</td><td align="center">1000</td></tr><tr><td align="center">4</td><td align="center">100</td><td align="center">9</td><td align="center">1001</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="2-常见的进制"><a href="#2-常见的进制" class="headerlink" title="2.常见的进制"></a>2.常见的进制</h2><ol><li>二进制：0~1，代码中以0b开头；</li><li>八进制：0~7，代码中以0开头；</li><li>十进制：0~9，前面不加前缀；</li><li>十六进制：0<del>9和a</del>f，代码中以0x开头；</li></ol><h2 id="3-任意进制转十进制"><a href="#3-任意进制转十进制" class="headerlink" title="3.任意进制转十进制"></a>3.任意进制转十进制</h2><ol><li>公式：系数<em>基数的权次幂 相加<br>如:<br>二进制0b101&#x3D;1</em>2^2+0<em>2^1+1</em>2^0&#x3D;5<br>八进制0101&#x3D;1<em>8^2+0</em>8^1+1<em>8^0&#x3D;65<br>十六进制0x101&#x3D;1</em>16^2+0<em>16^1+1</em>16^0&#x3D;257</li><li>二进制转十进制<br>8421快速转换法：</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th align="center">二进制</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th><th align="center">1</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">十进制</td><td align="center">128</td><td align="center">64</td><td align="center">32</td><td align="center">16</td><td align="center">8</td><td align="center">4</td><td align="center">2</td><td align="center">1</td></tr></tbody></table><ol start="3"><li>十进制转其他进制<br>除基取余法：不断地除以基数得到余数，直到商为0，再将余数倒着拼接起来</li></ol><p><img src="/../images/02%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AD%A6Java01Java%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/%E7%9F%AD%E9%99%A4%E6%B3%95.png" alt="Alt text"></p><h2 id="4-计算机的存储规则"><a href="#4-计算机的存储规则" class="headerlink" title="4.计算机的存储规则"></a>4.计算机的存储规则</h2><ol><li>GB2312编码：1981年5月1日发布的简体中文汉字编码国家标准。收录7445个图形字符，其中包括6763个汉字。</li><li>BIG5编码：台湾地区繁体中文标准字符集，共收录13053个中文字，1984年实施。</li><li>GBK编码：2000年3月17日发布，收录21003个汉字，包含国家标准GB13000-1中的全部中日韩汉字，和BIG5编码中的所有汉字。</li><li>Unicode编码：国际标准字符集，它将世界各种语言的每个字符定义一个唯一的编码，以满足跨语言、跨平台的文本信息转换。</li></ol><h2 id="5-图片"><a href="#5-图片" class="headerlink" title="5.图片"></a>5.图片</h2><p><strong>通过每一个像素点中的RGB三原色来存储</strong></p><ol><li>计算机三原色：红绿蓝RGB</li><li>可以写为十进制，如（255，255，255）</li><li>也可以写成十六进制，如（FFFFFF）</li></ol><h2 id="6-声音数据"><a href="#6-声音数据" class="headerlink" title="6.声音数据"></a>6.声音数据</h2><p>对声音的波形图进行采样再存储</p><h1 id="六、数据类型"><a href="#六、数据类型" class="headerlink" title="六、数据类型"></a>六、数据类型</h1><h2 id="1-基本数据类型"><a href="#1-基本数据类型" class="headerlink" title="1.基本数据类型"></a>1.基本数据类型</h2><p><img src="/../images/02%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AD%A6Java01Java%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B.png" alt="Alt text"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableDemo3</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//byte</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">byte</span> <span class="variable">b</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(b);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//short</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">short</span> <span class="variable">s</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(s);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//int </span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">30</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(i);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//long</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//如果要定义long类型的变量，需要在数据值后面加一个L作为后缀，可以是大写也可以是小写。建议大写。</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">long</span> <span class="variable">n</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">999999999L</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(n);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//float,后缀F</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">float</span> <span class="variable">f</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">10.1F</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(f);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//double</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">double</span> <span class="variable">d</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">20.2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(d);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//char</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">char</span> <span class="variable">c</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;中&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(c);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//boolean</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//true false</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="variable">o</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(o);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-练习"><a href="#2-练习" class="headerlink" title="2.练习"></a>2.练习</h2><ol><li><p>练习1：输出老师信息<br>姓名：黑马谢广坤<br>年龄：18<br>性别：男<br>身高：180.1<br>是否单身：是</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableTest2</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录姓名</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">name</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;黑马谢广坤&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录年龄</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">age</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录性别</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">char</span> <span class="variable">gender</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;男&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录身高</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">double</span> <span class="variable">height</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">180.1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录是否单身</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="variable">flag</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//输出变量的值</span></span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(name);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(age);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(gender);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(height);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(flag);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>练习2：输出电影信息<br>   电影名称：送初恋回家<br>   主演：刘鑫 张雨提 高媛<br>   导演：刘国彤<br>   类型：爱情<br>   年份：2020<br>   评分9.0</p>   <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableTest3</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录电影名</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">name</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;送初恋回家&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录主演名字</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">tostar</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;刘鑫 张雨提 高媛&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录导演</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">director</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;刘国彤&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录年份</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">year</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2020</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录电影评分</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">double</span> <span class="variable">grade</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">9.0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//输出变量的值</span></span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(name);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(tostar);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(director);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(year);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(grade);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>练习3：输出商品信息<br>   手机品牌：华为<br>   手机价格：5299.0</p>   <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">VariableTest3</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录手机品牌</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">name</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;华为&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//定义变量记录手机价格</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="type">double</span> <span class="variable">price</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">5299.0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//输出变量的值</span></span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(name);</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(price);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="七、标识符"><a href="#七、标识符" class="headerlink" title="七、标识符"></a>七、标识符</h1><p><strong>标识符：就是给类，方法，变量起的名字</strong></p><ol><li>标识符命名规则–硬性要求<ol><li>由数字、字母、下划线(_)和美元符($)组成</li><li>不能以数字开头</li><li>不能是关键字</li><li>区分大小写</li></ol></li><li>标识符命名规则–软性要求<ol><li>小驼峰命名法：方法、变量<ol><li>标识符是一个单词的时候，全部小写，如name;</li><li>标识符由多个单词组成的时候，第一个单词首字母小写，其余字母首字母大写，如firstName</li></ol></li><li>大驼峰命名法：类名<ol><li>标识符是一个单词时，首字母大写，如Student;</li><li>标识符由多个单词组成时，每个单词的首字母大写，如GoodStudent</li></ol></li></ol></li></ol><h1 id="八、键盘录入"><a href="#八、键盘录入" class="headerlink" title="八、键盘录入"></a>八、键盘录入</h1><p><strong>Java帮我们写好一个类叫Scanner,这个类就可以接受键盘输入的数字</strong>  </p><p>步骤一：导包–Scanner这个类在哪儿  </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//导包动作必须出现在类定义上边</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>步骤二：创建对象–表示我要开始用Scanner这个类了</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">Scanner</span> <span class="variable">sc</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Scanner</span>(System.in);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//上面这个格式里，只有sc是变量名，可以变，其余都不可以变</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>步骤三：接收数据–真正开始干活了</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//左边这个格式里面，只有i是变量名，可以变，其余的都不允许变</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>练习1：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1.导包</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ScannerDemo1</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//2.创建对象</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Scanner</span> <span class="variable">sc</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Scanner</span>(System.in);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入：&quot;</span>)；</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//3.接收数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(i);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>练习2：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1.导包</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ScannerDemo2</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//2.创建对象</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Scanner</span> <span class="variable">sc</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Scanner</span>(System.in);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//3.接收数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第一个数字：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第二个数字：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">j</span> <span class="operator">=</span> sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(i + j);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="九、IDEA"><a href="#九、IDEA" class="headerlink" title="九、IDEA"></a>九、IDEA</h1><h2 id="IDEA项目结构介绍"><a href="#IDEA项目结构介绍" class="headerlink" title="IDEA项目结构介绍"></a>IDEA项目结构介绍</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">project（项目）  </span><br><span class="line">    module（模块）  </span><br><span class="line">        package（包）  </span><br><span class="line">            class（类）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
